{"tid":1911353,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(走 咱們回家) 中囯衣業衣村部：草地貪夜蛾已經入侵中国","createTime":"2020-03-05T09:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T09:51:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ff10e85a1bc4e9e076d38c266cafef3a3ed2df3d","tid":1911353,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:24:48.000Z","msg":"據中國新聞網消息，5日，中國國務院聯防聯控機制召開新聞發布會。農業農村部種植業管理司司長潘文博表示，草地貪夜蛾確實已經入侵中國。<br />\n<br />\n  草地貪夜蛾原發於美洲熱帶和亞熱帶地區，去年首次入侵中國，主要發生在西南和華南，經全力防控，實際危害面積在240萬畝左右，蟲害地區產量損失控制在5%以內。<br />\n<br />\n  專家分析認為，草地貪夜蛾在西南和華南適宜生存，它成為又一個北遷南回、周年循環的重大遷飛性害蟲。據監測，今年草地貪夜蛾基數大，北遷時間要提早，預計是一個重發生的態勢。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2020/0305/812593.shtml</code></pre>"},{"pid":"67951883a26eedaf1a7bac6809d66ef49c338a33","tid":1911353,"uid":207543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XxRaAcv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXxRaAcv.jpg&h=9ea80a19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KwBaAcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwBaAcw.jpg&h=63b92bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#8Mar #將軍澳 #悼念會 #周同學<br />\n【梓樂悼念會】<br />\n日期 : 3月8日 (日)<br />\n時間 : 19:30 (20:09分默哀)<br />\n地點 : 將軍澳 尚十<br />\n*請自備蠟燭鮮花 , 及戴口罩<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3018832514817307&amp;set=gm.1240521269478455&amp;type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D3018832514817307%26set%3Dgm.1240521269478455%26type%3D3&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=a3e5aaa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3018832514817307&amp;set=gm.1240521269478455&amp;type=3</a>"},{"pid":"3dc9a8af98dc7019bcb23415c90dbac54e4c1a29","tid":1911353,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c52476d270d567d8c074e09f278b71db988369","tid":1911353,"uid":25100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:34:32.000Z","msg":"又蛾又蝗蟲 <br />\n咁頻能頂得住冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b505b2371877deb239024ce68717455281970a","tid":1911353,"uid":332804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:49:48.000Z","msg":"草地貪夜蛾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林奠貪月蛾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ace45e37ce3f7f9b6514fc4eb6ec375b59fe36","tid":1911353,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"咩草地月蛾呀？夜晚先出沒？"},{"pid":"fbca41a7e078dd497ff16b316711018d0151031e","tid":1911353,"uid":175108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6ace45e37ce3f7f9b6514fc4eb6ec375b59fe36","tid":1911353,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"咩草地月蛾呀？夜晚先出沒？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"即係月蛾"},{"pid":"26670ac83dcd9743f2151fd65758886cc70188a0","tid":1911353,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbca41a7e078dd497ff16b316711018d0151031e","tid":1911353,"uid":175108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6ace45e37ce3f7f9b6514fc4eb6ec375b59fe36","tid":1911353,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"咩草地月蛾呀？夜晚先出沒？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"即係月蛾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T09:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}